rComments: Professor Priestley gave me a purpose and, identity at the  University of Toronto. Now so many years later, I am a professor too! Thank you for inspiring me Professor Priestley!

I recorded all his classes.  I heard legends of his class, and I and so glad that I was able to take his class.  Book early for this class.  He teaches very difficult material well.  This was my favorite class and teacher during my undergrad.
once you get past his no-eyelash stare, you love him.  he's funny, calm, brilliant.  and his class will prolly change your life.  NEVER sell your copy of Chuangtzu, you'll regret it.
I'm now a graduate student, which means I've almost been in university for 10 years, and I dont think I've had a better prof: he embodies the best of what you'd want in a teacher.
The best class I've had in my life!! An extremely enriching class taught by an excellent instructor! Felt almost enlightened myself after this class!!
i took this course with priestley over 4 yrs ago, changed my outlook on life.
such presence...one could hear a pin drop, no due dates, great email response ra
An amazing teacher! One of the best at UofT!
the legend has brought many insight into Eastern phil. Reason to B at UT
This prtofessor is amazing and compassionate. The best at UoT!
A very friendly and enlightening man.  He was a wonderful teacher!
